snippet.title: Chicago 90 gameplay (PC Game, 1989)
snippet.description:
Gameplay for Chicago 90, Dos PC game produced by Microids in 1989 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/chicago-90/3928/
In this video I am playing as both a gangster and a cop and driving around the city. If you ever feel the need to go loose on the streets, this game allows you to do it.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
